     <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Giftige stoffer</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 4\" border=\"no\" name=\"f3b4c297-5ddf-4307-b1b0-3d52b786a527\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_3.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Ætsende stoffer</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 5\" border=\"no\" name=\"90b2360f-0db4-4456-a230-38cf58a99b17\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_4.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Radioaktive stoffer</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 6\" border=\"no\" name=\"50f6d587-0388-4812-b05f-994fedaef567\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_5.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Kran i arbejde</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 7\" border=\"no\" name=\"318e7afa-b2bd-4168-bdd4-b85b5ada3325\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_6.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Pas på kørende transport</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 8\" border=\"no\" name=\"7d3f5003-ed0b-4186-b758-89ff1a4dff4f\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_7.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Farlig elektrisk spænding</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <img alt=\"figur 9\" border=\"no\" name=\"e48de850-5570-498c-ab01-ca9f63e3a1e1\" src=\"/image.aspx?id=169925&img=BE6256_4_8.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">Giv agt *</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>*Dette skilt må ikke anvendes til advarsel mod farlige kemiske stoffer eller blandinger, medmindre skiltet anvendes i overensstemmelse med bilag 8, punkt 5.1, til at angive oplagring af farlige stoffer eller blandinger.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"310\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"116px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"116px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:6px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.2cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.2cm;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.2cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.2cm;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.2cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.2cm;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt none #000000;border-right: 1pt none #000000;border-top: 1pt none #000000;border-bottom: 1pt none #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.2cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.2cm;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt no